The paper involves the use of deep reinforcement learning for job scheduling in data center networks, which falls under the category of machine learning (cs.LG). It also deals with resource allocation and optimization in distributed systems, which is a topic in distributed, parallel, and cluster computing (cs.DC). The use of reinforcement learning also falls under the category of artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The paper also involves the use of neural networks, which is a topic in systems and control (cs.SY) and neural and evolutionary computing (cs.NE).
